Updates in Version 1.2022 of the NCCN Guidelines for Breast Cancer from Version 8.2021 include:

BINV-L (8 of 9) • HER2-Positive, Useful in Certain Circumstances, added: Neratinib
◊ 120 mg PO daily on days 1–7; Followed by: ◊ 160 mg PO daily on days 8–14; Followed by: ◊ 240 mg PO daily on days 15–28
