21-gene (Oncotype Dx) (for postmenopausal patients with pN0 and pN1 [1–3 positive nodes])c 21-gene (Oncotype Dx) (for premenopausal patients: pN0) 21-gene (Oncotype Dx) (for premenopausal patients with 1–3 positive nodes)c

